      <title>法国警告称，高温引发用水限制，将削减核电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/france-warns-of-nuclear-power-cuts-as-heat-triggers-water-curbs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于炎热的天气限制了排入罗纳河的水量，法国电力公司可能从本周末开始减少核反应堆的产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/france-warns-of-nuclear-power-cuts-as-heat-triggers-water-curbs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:31:11 GMT</pubDate>
