    <item>
      <title>塞浦路斯银行将重返希腊交易所并退出伦敦交易所</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/bank-of-cyprus-set-to-return-to-greek-exchange-quitting-london</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞浦路斯银行控股有限公司 (Bank of Cyprus Holdings Plc) 计划将其主要上市地点从伦敦证券交易所移回雅典证券交易所，以吸引新的投资者，该国最大的银行表示。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/bank-of-cyprus-set-to-return-to-greek-exchange-quitting-london</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>匈牙利通胀加速，进一步降息空间缩小</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hungary-inflation-accelerates-narrowing-room-for-more-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利通胀率小幅上升，突破了央行容忍区间的上限，缩小了持续一年多的货币宽松周期的延续空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hungary-inflation-accelerates-narrowing-room-for-more-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚鲁托在抗议活动再度升温的阴影下宣誓就任内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管肯尼亚民众威胁要重启反政府抗议活动，且该抗议活动已导致数十人丧生，但肯尼亚总统威廉·鲁托 (William Ruto) 仍经议会批准任命了 19 名部长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/kenya-s-ruto-swears-in-cabinet-in-shadow-of-renewed-protests</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:24:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿美寻求更多中国交易以推动石油化工业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/saudi-aramco-seeks-more-china-deals-in-oil-to-chemicals-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿美公司计划今年和明年在中国投资更多化工厂，以扩大其在中国已达成的交易，从而确保其原油的长期买家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/saudi-aramco-seeks-more-china-deals-in-oil-to-chemicals-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:11:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东和非洲展望 08/08/2024</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/horizons-middle-east-africa-08-08-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场仍动荡不安，投资者正在评估政策、地缘政治和经济衰退风险；中东局势紧张，油价上涨。本期节目还采访了约翰内斯堡证券交易所的首席执行官，该公司正努力吸引上市，以及阿布扎比国家石油公司物流和服务公司的首席财务官，该公司正努力推动盈利和全球扩张。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-08-08/horizons-middle-east-africa-08-08-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 06:10:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uniper 将在俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司裁决后向柏林支付约 29 亿欧元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uniper-adds-540-million-in-provisions-after-gazprom-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Uniper SE 能够用取消的对俄罗斯天然气工业股份公司 (Gazprom PJSC) 的付款义务抵消其所欠的损害赔偿后，该公司未来向德国政府支付的金额将增至约 29 亿欧元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/uniper-adds-540-million-in-provisions-after-gazprom-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ION Analytics 在市场波动中搁置 5 亿美元贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/ion-analytics-shelves-500-million-loan-deal-amid-market-swings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ION Analytics 是安德里亚·皮格纳塔罗 (Andrea Pignataro) ION 集团旗下的一个子公司，该公司停止了自 7 月底以来一直向投资者推销的 5 亿美元杠杆贷款交易，这表明信贷市场持续存在紧张情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/ion-analytics-shelves-500-million-loan-deal-amid-market-swings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场等待伊朗报复，油价维持反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在创下一周最大涨幅后趋于稳定，市场担心伊朗可能对以色列实施报复性打击，以报复暗杀哈马斯和真主党领导人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 23:16:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元走强导致日本股市下跌，美国股市下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/nikkei-futures-point-to-lower-japan-open-after-us-shares-falter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于日元走强和美国股市快速回落，抑制了对高风险资产的需求，日本股市下跌，结束了连续两天的上涨势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-07/nikkei-futures-point-to-lower-japan-open-after-us-shares-falter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 22:47:44 GMT</pubDate>
